"Understood." LORD ELDER said after a short pause. "You are the ones
who are there. Let me know what I can do for you to help you."

Of course there was not much that LORD ELDER could do from where he
was at but to offer advise. it would be up to PERCETOR, WINDLORD, and
NIGHTSHIFT to figure out what to do.

From down the tunnel the sound of some sort of metal on stone
bangining could be heard. It could have been digging or perhaps some
sort of mining work going on deep in the tunnels.

Then the sounds of something or someone giving command, it almost
sounded like english. But English would not appear on planet Earth for
several million years. What could be happening.

(TAG)

- Preston
